    a: 'GEO results vary depending on how much entity authority you already have and how competitive your topic area is. Technical and structural changes — like implementing schema markup and restructuring content — can begin to show results within weeks. Building broader entity authority across knowledge bases takes longer, typically three to six months of consistent effort, before it meaningfully affects AI citation frequency.',
